duktory-vx\" class=\"rks-link text-default hover:text-primary\">Reproduktory (VX)<span class=\"text-muted text-xs ml-2\">2</span></a></li></ul></li></ul></li><li class=\"rks-li\"><a href=\"/katalog-produktov/kategoria/varovacie-a-vyrozumievacie-systemy\" class=\"rks-link text-default hover:text-primary\">Varovacie a vyrozumievacie systémy<span class=\"text-muted text-xs ml-2\">5</span></a><details class=\"rks-disc\"><summary class=\"rks-arrow\" aria-label=\"Rozbaliť\"></summary></details><ul class=\"rks-children pl-3 mt-1 space-y-1 border-l border-gray-200\"><li class=\"rks-leaf\"><a href=\"/katalog-produktov/kategoria/elektronicke-sireny\" class=\"rks-link text-default hover:text-primary\">Elektronické sirény<span class=\"text-muted text-xs ml-2\">5</span></a></li></ul></li></ul></nav>";
